snippet.title: Game Boy Advance Longplay [302] A Sound of Thunder (US)
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by: NPI

Isometric perspective makes it a bit painful to play, but the pixel sprites are great looking.

Video game based on the movie that is based on the sci-fi short story by Ray Bradbury, you know the one where a small butterfly brought from the past causes havoc in the present.

Developed as the last game by Moebius Entertainment in 2004, that later become Rockstar Leeds.
